e average number of"},{"type":"text","text":"[s3:rkja'ler{n]"},{"type":"text","text":"copies of a publication sold over a given period)"},{"type":"text","text":"circulatory （adj血液循环的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"reputation","headword":"reputation"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 名声(good name)"},{"type":"text","text":"[repju'ter[n]"},{"type":"text","text":"Although he had the numerous films to his credit and a reputation for technical"},{"type":"text","text":"expertise, the moviemaker lacked originality: all his films were sadly derivative of"},{"type":"text","text":"the work of others."},{"type":"entry","text":"discriminate","headword":"discriminate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. [区别,歧视(to make a clear distinction)"},{"type":"text","text":"[dr'skriminert]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：dis（分开）+crimin（区别）+ate→区别（对待）→区别，歧视"},{"type":"text","text":"undiscriminating (adj. 无鉴别力的);discriminating （adj. 有辨别力的)"}]},{"number":176,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 14 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"archaeological","headword":"archaeological"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj考古学的"},{"type":"text","text":"[a:rkia'la:dzrkl]"},{"type":"text","text":"archaeologist（n.考古学家）;archaeology（n.考古学）"},{"type":"entry","text":"certainty","headword":"certainty"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.确定的事情（thing that is certain)"},{"type":"text","text":"['ssirtnti]"},{"type":"text","text":"来自certain（adj确定的，必然的）"},{"type":"text","text":"uncertainty (n.犹豫；迟疑)"},{"type":"entry","text":"approximate","headword":"approximate"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj近似的，大约的（much ike;nearly correct or exact)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'pra:ksimat]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：ap（去）+proxim（接近）+ate→近似的，大约的"},{"type":"text","text":"图approximation（n.近似值；粗略估算）"},{"type":"entry","text":"immutability","headword":"immutability"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.不变，不变性（the quality of being incapable of mutation)"},{"type":"text","text":"[1,mju:ta'brlati]"},{"type":"text","text":"mutability（n.易变性；性情不定）"},{"type":"ent