","text":"n.倡导者，拥护者（proponent)"},{"type":"text","text":"[pra'taeganrst]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：prot（看作proto，第一）+agon（斗争）+ist→率先引起争斗→倡导者"},{"type":"entry","text":"apex","headword":"apex"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.顶点，最高点（peak，vertex）"},{"type":"text","text":"['erpeks]"},{"type":"text","text":"图reach the apex达到顶点"},{"type":"text","text":"acme, climax, crest, crown, fastigium"}]},{"number":179,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"dexterity","headword":"dexterity"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.纯熟，灵巧（skill in using one's hands or body:"},{"type":"text","text":"[dek'sterati]"},{"type":"text","text":"adroitness)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：dexter（右）+ity→像右手一样→纯熟，灵巧"},{"type":"entry","text":"peak","headword":"peak"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.变得低悴，消瘦(to become thin or sick; emaciate)"},{"type":"text","text":"[pi:k]"},{"type":"text","text":"peak and pine 悼"},{"type":"entry","text":"negotiate","headword":"negotiate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v协商，商定，议定（to arrange for or bring about through conference，discussion,"},{"type":"text","text":"[nr'gaufiert]"},{"type":"text","text":"and compromise)"},{"type":"text","text":"留 The actual rigidity of Wilson's position was always betrayed by his refusal to"},{"type":"text","text":"compromise after having initially agreed to negotiare a settlement."},{"type":"entry","text":"cOW","headword":"cOW"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 母牛 v威胁(to threat)"},{"type":"text","text":"[kau]"},{"type":"entry","text":"fatal","headword":"fatal"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.致命的(causing death);灾难性的(causing disaster)"},{"type":"text","text":"[fertl]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自fate（n.命运）"},{"type":"entry","text":"subsist","headword":"subsist"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.生存下去：继续存在（toexist)：维持生活"},{"type":"text","text":"[sab'sist]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：sub（下面）+sist（站）→站下去，活下去→生存下去"},{"type":"entry","text":"pregnant","headword":"pregnant"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.怀孕的(gravid);充满的(full, teeming)"},{"type":"text","text":"['pregnant]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：pre（在前面）+gn（出生）+ant→尚未出生的→怀孕的"},{"type":"entry","text":"glacial","headword":"glacial"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 冰河期的(of the Ice Age); 寒冷的(very cold)"},{"type":"text","text":"['glerj/]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：glaci（冰）+al→冰河期的"},{"type":"entry","text":"lionize","headword":"lionize"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 崇拜,看重(to treat as an object of great interest or importance)"},{"type":"text","text":"['laranaiz]"},{"type":"text","text":"国联想记忆：lon（狮子：名流）+ize→视为名流→崇拜"},{"type":"text","text":"图lionization (n.崇拜)"},{"type":"text","text":"exhaust"},{"type":"entry","text":"revolt","headword":"revolt"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.反叛，造反（to renounce allegiance or subjection;rebel);反感，厌恶(to tum"},{"type":"text","text":"[rr'vault]"},{"type":"text","text":"away with disgust)"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：re（反）+volt（转）→反过来转→反叛"},{"type":"entry","text":"assess","headword":"assess"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.评定，核定(to evaluate)：估计，估价(to estimate the quality)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'ses]"},{"type":"text","text":"assessment(n.估价，评价）"},{"type":"entry","text":"sap","headword":"sap"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 树液(the waitery fluid thait circulates through a plant); 活力(vigor, vitality) v 前,"},{"type":"text","text":"[saep]"}]},{"number":180,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 14 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"extant","headword":"extant"},{"type":"text","text":"adfj.现存的，现有的（currently or actually existing)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ek'staent]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：ex+tant（看作stand，站）→站出来→现存的"},{"type":"entry","text":"confer","headword":"confer"},{"type":"text","text":"商议，商谈（to have discussions)：授予，赋予（toreward to）"},{"type":"text","text":"[kan'fs:r]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：con（共同）+fer（带来，拿来）→共同带来观点→商谈"},{"type":"entry","text":"colloquial","headword":"colloquial"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.口语的，口头的(conversational)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ka'laukwial]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：col（共同）+loqu（说话）+ial→共同说的→口语的"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 使出神，使入迷(to fill with great wonder and delight as if by magic)"},{"type":"entry","text":"entrance","headword":"entrance"},{"type":"text","text":"['entrans]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自enter（v进入）"},{"type":"entry","text":"aristocracy","headword":"aristocracy"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 贵族(the people of the highest social class especially from noble families)：贵"},{"type":"text","text":"[aerr'sta:krasi]"},{"type":"text","text":"族政府，贵族统治(government in which power is held by the nobility)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：aristo（最好的）+cracy（统治）→贵族统治"},{"type":"text","text":"aristocratic(adj.贵族的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"nonsensical","headword":"nonsensical"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 无意义的(having no meaning or conveying no intelligible ideas);荒谬的"},{"type":"text","text":"[na:n'sensrkl]"},{"type":"text","text":"(absurd)"},{"type":"entry","text":"rhetorical","headword":"rhetorical"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj修辞的，修辞学的（of,relating to,or concerned with rhetoric)：虚夸的，辞藻"},{"type":"text","text":"[rr't:rikl]"},{"type":"text","text":"华丽的9(characterized by overelaborate or bombastic rhetoric)"},{"type":"entry","text":"manipulate","headword":"manipulate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. (熟练地）操作，处理(to operate or control;handlle)"},{"type":"text","text":"manipulate"},{"type":"text","text":"[ma'nrpjulert]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：mani（手）+pul（拉）+ate→用手拉→（熟练地）操"},{"type":"text","text":"作，处理"},{"type":"text","text":"By dint of much practice in the laboratory. the"},{"type":"text","text":"anatomy student became ambidextrous and was able to"},{"type":"text","text":"manipu/ate her dissecting tools with either hand."},{"type":"entry","text":"fickleness","headword":"fickleness"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.浮躁：变化无常"},{"type":"text","text":"['fiklnas]"},{"type":"entry","text":"inconstancy","headword":"inconstancy"},{"type":"text","text":"好！就用你"},{"type":"entry","text":"prestigious","headword":"prestigious"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.有名望的，有威望的(having prestige;honored)"},{"type":"text","text":"[pre'stidsas]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自prestige（声望，威望）"},{"type":"text","text":"留 Many of the early Hollywood moguls sought to aggrandize themselves and"},{"type":"text","text":"enhance their celluloid empires by snaring prestigious writers and intellectuals"}]},{"number":181,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"<<<GRE词汇精选乱序版"},{"type":"entry","text":"repetitive","headword":"repetitive"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj重复的(repetitious);反复性的(containing repetition)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ri'petativ]"},{"type":"text","text":"图来自repeat（v重复）"},{"type":"entry","text":"comic","headword":"comic"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.可笑的：喜剧的（using comedy)n.喜剧演员（comedian）"},{"type":"text","text":"[ka:mrk]"},{"type":"text","text":"an inventive comic actor一位有创造力的喜剧演员"},{"type":"entry","text":"recede","headword":"recede"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.后退，撤回(to move back; withdraw)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rr'si:d]"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：re（向后）+ced（走）+e→后退"},{"type":"entry","text":"punishment","headword":"punishment"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.惩罚，刑罚(suffering, pain, or loss that serves as retribution);虐待(severe,"},{"type":"text","text":"['panx{mant]"},{"type":"text","text":"rough, or disastrous treatment)"},{"type":"definition","text":"A sense of fairness dictates that the punishment should fit the crime; yet,"},{"type":"text","text":"in actual practice, judicial decisions vary greatly for the same type of criminal"},{"type":"text","text":"offense."},{"type":"entry","text":"unworldly","headword":"unworldly"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 非世俗的(not swayed by mundane considerations);精神上的(spiritual)"},{"type":"text","text":"[An'w3:rldli]"},{"type":"note","text":"图联想记忆：un（不)+worldly（世俗的）→非世俗的"},{"type":"text","text":"Without seeming unworlclly, Wiliam James appeared wholly removed from the"},{"type":"text","text":"commonplaces of society, the conventionality of academy."},{"type":"entry","text":"conformity","headword":"conformity"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.—致；遵从，顺从(action in accordance with some specified standard or"},{"type":"text","text":"[kan'fo:rmati]"},{"type":"text","text":"authority)"},{"type":"entry","text":"implausible","headword":"implausible"},{"type":"text","text":"adfj. 难以置信的(not plausible)"},{"type":"text","text":"[m'pl:zabl]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：im（不）+plausible（可信的）→难以置信的"},{"type":"entry","text":"nonchalance","headword":"nonchalance"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 冷漠，冷淡(the quality or state of being nonchalant;"},{"type":"text","text":"modest"},{"type":"text","text":"[nanfa'la:ns]"},{"type":"text","text":"casual lack of concern)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：non（不）+chal（关心）+ance→不关心→无动于衷→冷漠"},{"type":"text","text":"Despite an affected nonchalance which convinced casual observers that he"},{"type":"example","text":"was indlifferent about his painting and enjoyed only frivolity. Warhol cared deeply"},{"type":"text","text":"about his art and labored at it diligently."},{"type":"entry","text":"commentary","headword":"commentary"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.实况报道（spoken description of an event as it"},{"type":"text","text":"[ka:manteri]"},{"type":"text","text":"happens); (对书等的)集注(set of explanatory notes on a"},{"type":"text","text":"book)"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：comment（评论）+ary→集注"},{"type":"entry","text":"territorial","headword":"territorial"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.领土的(of or relating to a territory);地方的(nearby"},{"type":"text","text":"[,tera't:rial]"},{"type":"text","text":"local)"},{"type":"text","text":"图 territorial economy 地方经济"},{"type":"text","text":"commentary"},{"type":"entry","text":"underground","headword":"underground"},{"type":"definition","text":"adv.在地下：秘密地(in or into hiding or secret operation) adj.地下的：秘密的"},{"type":"text","text":"[Anda'graund]"},{"type":"text","text":"Just as astrology was for centuries an underground faith, countering the"}]},{"number":182,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 14 >>>"},{"type":"text","text":"defiance against the professional sciences."},{"type":"text","text":"subterranean, subterrestrial, underearth, underfoot"},{"type":"entry","text":"remunerative","headword":"remunerative"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.报酬高的，有利润的(providing payment:profitable)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rr'mju:naratrv]"},{"type":"text","text":"gainful, lucrative"},{"type":"entry","text":"amend","headword":"amend"},{"type":"definition","text":"v 改正,修正(to put right); 改善(to change or modify for the better)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'mend]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：a（加强）+mend（修理）→修正"},{"type":"entry","text":"profligacy","headword":"profligacy"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.放荡;肆意挥霍(the quality or state of being profligate)"},{"type":"text","text":"['pra:fligasi]"},{"type":"entry","text":"allusion","headword":"allusion"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.暗指，间接提到(an implied or indirect reference esp. in iterature)"},{"type":"text","text":"['lu:3n]"},{"type":"text","text":"图来自allude（v暗指，间接提到）"},{"type":"entry","text":"reverberate","headword":"reverberate"}]}]}